  "detailed_description": "In this turn-base strategy RPG, you can fight demons and Faye, make friends, give gifts, and save the world!<br><br>Story:<br>Shadow looms over the land causing the Faye to rampage! The Priestess calls upon her knights to resolve the problem. Peter, a skilled traveler with nothing better to do, joins the knights led by Kaine to stop the Shadow.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753690/extras/b8121542c08c05263ad40d9aa6b4fa90.avif?t=1750748021\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 15 chapters, and many optional battles!<br></li><li>Help Peter befriend allies and even Faye. Maybe he'll even find love!<br></li><li>Use your items or give them as gifts.<br></li><li>Levels and experience points are used by some abilities as an expendable resource.<br></li><li>A charming, classic visual style.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1753690/extras/e4da415d67ae45428d64b34cf2a03a96.avif?t=1750748021\" width=184 height=184 /></span>",
